product_name: AllExtreme EX40WF2 4 LED Fog Light Super Bright Spot Flood Beam Driving Lamp for Motorcycle Cars Bikes & SUV (40W, White Light, 2 PCS)
review_comment: timelinespurchased 16 jul 2020delivered 20 jul 2020installed 14 aug 2020kaput 04 sept 2020profile of reviewer after 25 years of riding driving and lakhs of kms 10k reviews pre ordering stage after borking at the price of offerings from maddog scout x auxiliary light i decided to take a punt on these allextreme ex40wf2 4 led fog light 40w white light 2 pcs very cheap at under rs 1400 for a pair i didn t have high expectations but they can t be that bad can they read on initial review post delivery out of the box the lights seem alright metal cases nice clear lenses and reasonable build quality however no good waterproof sealing for avoid water seaping inside there s okaish wiring with a bar mounted switch hooked up to a relay when plugged in these led chips produce a decent bright spot without drawing to much power specs say 30w max each so shouldn t overload your bike s charging system installation review switchwiring in was fairly straight forward though the loom was like the longest conga snake you ve ever seen the loom plugs direct into your battery via a relay triggered by the bar mounted switch do wire them in through a relay on a switched live to avoid getting a flat battery when you forget to turn them off initial review post installation on the road they ve turned out effective they certainly provide more light on dark roads great for spotting potholes and debris whether they get you noticed more is a difficult one to say when you start looking for other drivers noticing you you start attributing every twitch or glance to people spotting your bright new lights on the nh4 on a darkened monsoon road ownership review post 1 small ride 300kms they were as cheap as chips by no means perfect but alright enough to get by they may not last years but at this price they have to atleast last 1 year now the real story begins21 days in after installing the lights 1 pc of the pair go kaput on the nh4 in the middle of night while travelling backs to bangalore from pune yes i know people would say why travelling in pandemic times it was for a novel cause lets skip the posat story back to the ordeal the single pc along with the stock on my ktm 390 adv got me to bangalore somehow trying to diagnose what went wrong now we had to check if it is the relay wiring switch that has gone bad no all working fine with only the led light not working switched with another working piece all fine now it was the turn of the led lights to be check voila yes it was the capacitor inside led light that went kaboom not worth spending more time on repairing conclusion would i go for another luck on this kind of shopping involving risk that might lead to accident on any road due to low quality product i say nooo

product_name: Autofy 1 YEAR WARRANTY Universal Side Shooter LED Fog Light Bar Sideshooter Bike Fog light Auxillary Driving Lamp Work Aluminium SMD Fog Light For All Bikes Cars SUV (40W Black)
review_comment: disappointed is the only word to describe my experience with this product after spending so much time reading so many reviews and after considering so many options i narrowed down to this product only to be disappointed just out of the box brand new one of the light is okay but the other one is so dim and powerless and also it has a strong yellow amber spot at the center of its focus beam looking closely upon the unit itself all the leds of this unit are not at center of its reflector cones they are all alligned one sided also one of the led in this unit has a yellow amber rust colored junk sticking around it which i assume is the reason for the strong yellow amber spot it just proves one thing that there is no quality check whatsoever on this product if there indeed was a quality check how can an abruptly visible flaw malfunction like this go unnoticed disappointed so returning the product with products like these i think its pure chance as to what quality of units you get by chance you can get good units which explains the 4 ratings it enjoys on amazon and by chance like in my case you can get an abruptly bad unit which can make you totally disappointed and make you loose confidence trust on the brand itself as a whole so i cannot advise anyone whether to purchase or to avoid this product i can only wish whoever purchases gets good units

product_name: Autofy 1 YEAR WARRANTY Universal Side Shooter LED Fog Light Bar Sideshooter Bike Fog light Auxillary Driving Lamp Work Aluminium SMD Fog Light For All Bikes Cars SUV (40W Black)
review_title: one of the few purchases that has given me a genuine smile on my face
review_comment: autofy has outdone the competition by a 10 miles the packaging way beyond expectations i thought it the lights will come in crappy packing but autofy has done a fantastic job each of the lights was individually packed in clear wrap and bundled with a compatible bracket and needed nuts and bolts in a ziplock this was all wrapped in bubble wrap and then put in a box i mean if these lights were a phone the packaging would be like that of an iphone for the performance if you haven t seen the attached video yet please do these are super bright lights with more than enough throw and spread easy to fit comes with a switch and 6month warranty the build is sturdy and can take more than a few hits mind you no other brand in this price range offers any of these things a super easy 15 on 10 for this product from me autofy hats off to you and i hope you will make all my future purchases just as pleasant

product_name: Autofy 1 YEAR WARRANTY Universal Side Shooter LED Fog Light Bar Sideshooter Bike Fog light Auxillary Driving Lamp Work Aluminium SMD Fog Light For All Bikes Cars SUV (40W Black)
review_title: great product fits my lil offroader like a charm
